LAGOS – Allied Integrated Promotion and Management Limited (AIPM), organisers of the African Brand Innovators Award (AFRIBIA) in recognition of the most credible brands in the continent of Africa, has Scheduled the awards to hold on Friday 23 June 2023, at the Sheraton Hotel & Suites, Ikeja Lagos Nigeria. With the theme ‘Overcoming Brand Pitfalls In African Market’, the organisers extended invitations to distinguished corporate brands across five African States, and some top government functionaries to an awards ceremony that will feature a Conference, Sales, Interactive sessions, Networking and Presentations of Awards. Speaking on the importance of the Awards, Mr Obinna Ndukwe the secretary, organising committee, says, “It is imperative to Create and promote a Symbol for African brands as a way of easy recognition for top performing brands in Africa.”